    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Both arguments for supporting (or not) `Infinity` are valid. Dropping or adding complete support for infinite values is something we should consider in a next major release if it is to add breaking changes then.\r\n\r\nI'm going to document the usage of `undefined` as a \"no bound\" value for `refine()` since this is a priority 🙂",
